  "summary": "Understand the system before adding technology.",
  "body": "Many organizations attempt to solve systemic problems with additional features or tools.\n\nJoz prefers to understand:\n\n- incentives\n- workflows\n- ownership\n- bottlenecks\n- feedback loops\n- governance\n\nbefore introducing technology.\n\nAdding AI to a broken system often amplifies existing problems.\n\nImproving the system first usually creates more sustainable value.",
